Installation instructions

Install Redmine plugin:
script/plugin install git://github.com/bugherd/redmine_bugherd.git

Create a Project Custom Field called "BugHerd Project Key"
- Administration > Custom Fields > Projects
- Format: Text
- New custom field
- Name: BugHerd Project Key
- Untick "Visible" to ensure the value is not seen by anyone but project administrator

You are now ready to setup a project integration from within a BugHerd project.
